<a id='Will the Virtual Practicum be entirely remote (via Zoom)? Will there be an in-person component?'><b>Will the Virtual Practicum be entirely remote (via Zoom)? Will there be an in-person component?</b>
<p>Yes, our Virtual Practicum will be entirely remote, conducted via Zoom. Program staff will distribute Zoom links for the intro session, lectures and discussions, and Shark Tank as needed. Students are responsible for coordinating within their Shark Tank groups, but program staff will assist where possible. Course materials will be mailed to the address provided by students at start of the Practicum. At the time of this writing (January 2021), Brown University is not allowing visitors to campus for in-person programs.</p>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<a id='I have other commitments during the weekends; will these conflict with the Practicum?'><b>I have other commitments during the weekends; will these conflict with the Practicum?</b>
