<p>This is (kind of) a surprise! We will send you materials that you can use for hands-on exploration of bioluminescence and fluorescence. Make sure the address you provide is a location where you can receive your supplies within a few hours to a day. In other words, you don't need to be able to retrieve your package <i>immediately</i> after it is delivered, but it also shouldn't hang around for multiple days, especially if your package will be waiting outside and you live in a climate where it is very hot or very cold in February.</p>

